2026-05-11T04:49:16.2560836Z 13    <!--
2026-05-11T04:49:16.2561438Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-11T04:49:16.2562616Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
